OL,3,CNorthern leaders call for Avanti West
OL,4,CCoast train service to be nationalised
OL,6,FNorthern leaders have called for 's
OL,7,Ftrain services to be nationalised as
OL,8,Fits performance is "too short of
OL,9,Fexpectations".
OL,11,FTransport for the North (TfN), a body
OL,12,Fwhich provides advice to the
OL,13,FGovernment, passed a motion on
OL,14,FWednesday to urge Transport Secretary
OL,15,FMark Harper to terminate the
OL,16,Foperator's contract "at the earliest
OL,17,Fpossible opportunity".
