OL,3,CNorthern leaders call for Avanti West
OL,4,CCoast train service to be nationalised
OL,6,FIt wants the Department for
OL,7,FTransport's (DfT) Operator of Last
OL,8,FResort (OLR) to take on responsibility
OL,9,Ffor long-distance services on the West
OL,10,FCoast Main Line between London Euston
OL,11,Fand Scotland.
OL,13,FThe OLR already runs London North
OL,14,FEastern Railway, Northern,
OL,15,FSoutheastern and TransPennine Express.
