OL,3,CNorthern leaders call for Avanti West
OL,4,CCoast train service to be nationalised
OL,6,FLord McLoughlin, who chairs TfN and is
OL,7,Fa former transport secretary, said:
OL,8,F"Today's board was very clear. The
OL,9,Fperformance on the West Coast Main
OL,10,FLine by Avanti has been so poor for so
OL,11,Flong that action now must be taken.
OL,13,F"We will be writing statutory advice
OL,14,Ftoday to the Secretary of State
OL,15,Fcalling for Avanti to be relieved of
OL,16,Fits contract.
OL,18,F"The travelling public deserve a
OL,19,Fservice they can rely on, but Avanti
OL,20,Fhas fallen far too short of
OL,21,Fexpectations for far too long now."
