OL,3,CNorthern leaders call for Avanti West
OL,4,CCoast train service to be nationalised
OL,6,FA spokesperson for FirstGroup, which
OL,7,Fowns the operator, said: "Our team at
OL,8,FAvanti West Coast, and everyone
OL,9,Fconnected with the train operator, are
OL,10,Fall working hard with a singular focus
OL,11,Fon delivering the service that
OL,12,Fcustomers expect.
OL,14,F"In recent months the service has been
OL,15,Fbelow expectations on some days for a
OL,16,Fvariety of reasons, including driver
OL,17,Funavailability due to historic leave
OL,18,Fpolicies as well as elevated sickness
OL,19,Flevels.
