OL,6,F"Changing the operator won't affect
OL,7,Fthese fundamental issues affecting the
OL,8,Fservice, which is why it is vital that
OL,9,Fwe continue working with trade unions
OL,10,Fwith whom we have had recent positive
OL,11,Fdiscussions, and continue working with
OL,12,FGovernment and other stakeholders on
OL,13,Four plans to deliver long-term
OL,14,Fimprovements in customer experience,
OL,15,Fresilience and a new fleet."
