OL,3,CNorthern leaders call for Avanti West
OL,4,CCoast train service to be nationalised
OL,6,FRail minister Huw Merriman told the
OL,7,FCommons' Transport Select Committee
OL,8,Flast month that Avanti West Coast will
OL,9,F"never be able to deliver a proper
OL,10,Fservice" due to provisions in its
OL,11,Fdrivers' contracts relating to working
OL,12,Fpractices and booking time off.
OL,14,FHe said the operator's drivers cannot
OL,15,Fbe asked to do more than one return
OL,16,Fjourney per shift, and can book time
OL,17,Foff as little as 48 hours in advance.
