OL,3,CNorthern leaders call for Avanti West
OL,4,CCoast train service to be nationalised
OL,6,FIn September l2023, Avanti West
OL,7,FCoast's operating contract was renewed
OL,8,Fby the DfT for up to nine years, with
OL,9,FMr Harper claiming it was "back on
OL,10,Ftrack" following major disruption.
OL,12,FA Department for Transport
OL,13,Fspokesperson said: "Stripping Avanti's
OL,14,Fcontract would just cause more
OL,15,Fupheaval for passengers rather than
OL,16,Fsolving the challenges the operator is
OL,17,Ffacing.
OL,19,FThese include restrictive working
OL,20,Fpractices that can't be reformed
OL,21,Fwithout Aslef's agreement.
OL,26,@qD@[OUrD@FO]uD@TOU
