OL,3,CNorthern leaders call for Avanti West
OL,4,CCoast train service to be nationalised
OL,6,F"Following the Government's
OL,7,Fintervention to put the operator on
OL,8,Fsuccessive short-term contracts,
OL,9,FAvanti did make significant progress
OL,10,Fduring the first half of 2023.
OL,12,FHowever, improvements still need to be
OL,13,Fmade, which is why it's important the
OL,14,Foperator continues to address the
OL,15,Funderlying challenges it faces and the
OL,16,FGovernment continues to hold it to
OL,17,Faccount, if it doesn't."
